## Project-Specific Rules
- Main document in `report.md` (or specified in client brief)
- Supporting materials in `appendices/`
- Data/charts in `data/` with source references
- Keep sections <= 2,000 words (client readability)
- Use clear headings: # Executive Summary, ## Key Findings, ### Recommendation
- All numbers cited must have sources (footnotes or appendix references)
- Final draft review required before sending to client

## Deliverables
- Executive summary (1 page)
- Main report (10–20 pages typically)
- Appendices (charts, data, methodology)
- Optional: presentation slide deck

## Client Handoff
- PDF export with embedded fonts
- Clean formatting, no code or technical jargon unless explicitly requested
- Include table of contents and page numbers
- Review with client stakeholder before final send

